text: The Victors is a 1963 British American World War II movie directed by Carl Foreman and based on the novel The Human Kind by Alexander Baron. It stars Albert Finney, Vincent Edwards, George Hamilton, Eli Wallach, Maurice Ronet, George Peppard, Romy Schneider, Jeanne Moreau, Jim Mitchum, Mervyn Johns, Peter Fonda, Elke Sommer, Peter Vaughan and was distributed by Columbia Pictures. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1963 movies Category:American war movies Category:British movies Category:World War II movies
